name: Fio Germi (Metal Slug)
description:
I haven't played Metal Slug in so long...

So important note. You'll likely want the following in the negatives: holding weapon, holding gun

I also had 'arms up' in the negatives because I didn't think about why they were up in the first place haha

As Usual:
Trained on Anything v3
Demo is Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 0.9
The last two images are using my goth LoRA at weight 0.5 (Fio's LoRA is a bit heavy to mix with this one at a higher weight haha)

Goth Fio is a new favorite combo hahaha
